             was indicted for <rs id="t18180401-55-off315" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18180401-55-off315" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180401-55-off315" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18180401-55-cd316" type="crimeDate">20th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180401-55-off315 t18180401-55-cd316"></join>, 10 yards of woollen cloth, value 3l., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18180401-55-victim433" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Whitehead
                        <interp inst="t18180401-55-victim433" type="surname" value="Whitehead"></interp>
